| |                             | |       | |                             | |
| |   Welcome to my website!    | |       | |  John, we are logging out   | |
| |                             | |       | |  of the relying parties.    | |
| |                             | |       | |                             | |
| +-----------------------------+ |       | |  +~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~+  | |
| |   Sign-in to rp.example     | |       | |  :"<script>"             :  | |
| |     with idp.example?       | |       | |  :" IdentityCredential. ":  | |
| |                             | |       | |  :"    logoutRPs([{     ":  | |
| | .----.                      | |       | |  :"       url: ...      ":  | |
| | | :) | "John Doe"           | |  -->  | |  :"       accountId: ...":  | |
| | '----' "john@email.com"     | |       | |  :"    }, {             ":  | |
| |                             | |       | |  :"       ...           ":  | |
| | +-------------------------+ | |       | |  :"    }]);             ":  | |
| | |     Continue as John    | | |       | |  :"<\/script>"           :  | |
| | +------------+------------+ | |       | |  +~~~~~~~~~~~+~~~~~~~~~~~+  | |
| '--------------|--------------' |       | '--------------|--------------' |
'----------------|----------------'       '----------------|----------------'
                 |                                         |
                 |                                         |
                 |        +------------------------+       |        +-------+
